---

## Struktur Wiki (10 Kategori)

```
.claude/wiki/
├── README.md          ← Ini (index + conventions)
├── log.md             ← Reverse-chrono harvest/activity log
├── gotchas/           ← Pitfalls & traps — quick-ref (Problem/RootCause/Solution)
├── patterns/          ← Reusable code & design patterns (Context/Impl/Validation)
├── decisions/         ← ADR-light: decision records (Context/Decision/Rationale)
├── context/           ← Background, sejarah, FYI, info project
├── config/            ← Setup, env, konfigurasi, install notes
├── learnings/         ← Lessons learned, insights, discovery
├── errors/            ← Error & bug catalog (ORA-*, PHP warnings, dll)
├── implementation/    ← How-it-works, cara kerja komponen
├── optimization/      ← Performance, caching, tuning notes
├── test/              ← Test strategy, coverage notes, assertion patterns
└── entities/          ← Per-entity notes (services, modules, external APIs)
```

---

## Linking Convention

Gunakan `[[double-bracket]]` untuk wiki refs:
- `[[gotchas/oracle-oci8-connect]]` → `.claude/wiki/gotchas/oracle-oci8-connect.md`
- `[[patterns/repository-pattern]]`
- `[[decisions/use-oracle-over-mysql]]`
- `[[entities/auth-service]]`

Regular markdown links `[text](url)` untuk external links — tidak dianggap wiki refs.

---

## Cara Pakai

**Tambah entry manual:**
```
Buat .claude/wiki/<kategori>/YYYY-MM-DD-<slug>.md
```

**Harvest dari project lain:**
```
/knowledge-harvest --source <path>
```

**Cek konsistensi:**
```
/wiki-lint
```
Output: broken refs, orphan files, missing front pages.

**Promote ke parent workspace:**
```
/memory-promote gotchas/<filename>
```

